    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以PatientRecords是起点，先进入IDLE状态。那从IDLE到WRITING的触发条件是什么？是用户操作还是系统事件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是AW握手，也就是认证写入的握手协议。触发时要标注来源是PatientRecords本身。另外写入完成后需要回到IDLE，这个由EMR_Sync模块来触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "AW handshake",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "W complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先用stateDiagram-v2画一下：PatientRecords指向IDLE作为初始状态，IDLE到WRITING标注AW handshake，WRITING返回IDLE标注W complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "AW handshake",
        "W complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构是对的，但标注里要加上模块来源，比如AW handshake后面注明来自PatientRecords，W complete注明来自EMR_Sync，这样审计时能追溯。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AW handshake",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "W complete",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下标注格式，用括号把来源模块括起来。另外图标题我打算用HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，符合合规审计的命名规范。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "AW handshake",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "W complete",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，HIPAA_Vault的命名没问题。再确认一下：IDLE只能由PatientRecords自己触发进入WRITING，而退出WRITING必须由EMR_Sync确认同步完成，这个权限分离是正确的。",
      "elements_involved": [
